quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  26,207,"Na di kiran makalinding so piyakisawitan kiran a kapipiya gi­nawa!"
  26,208,"Na da-a bininasa Mi a Phagingud, a ba da-a Miyamakaik­ tiyar ron"
  26,209,"Pananadum; na kuna a ba Kami manga salimbot."
  26,210,"Go kuna a ba Initoron Sukaniyan o manga Shaitan:"
  26,211,"Go di kiran patot, go di ran khagaga."
  26,212,"Mata-an! A siran na so kapamamakinug (ko Langit) na piyakigunukan kiran ndun."
  26,213,"Na di Ka Phanongganoi sa pud o Allah, a Tohan a salakao ka Mabaloi Ka a pud ko phangasi­ siksa."
  26,214,"Na Paka-iktiyarangka so manga Tonganaingka, a manga da­ dasug,"
  26,215,"Go Paka-inayangka so Go­ wagowaingka ko tao a Miyonot Ruka, a pud ko Miyamaratiyaya."
  26,216,"Na amai ka Sorangungka iran, na Tharowangka: A Mata-an! A Sakun na angiyas Ako ko gi-i niyo nggolaola-an!"
  26,217,"Go Panarig Ka ko (Allah a) Mabagur, a Makalimo-on,-"
  26,218,"A so puphakailai Ruka ko masa a Kaputhindug Ka,"
  26,219,"Go so Kapuphagukaskas Ka a rakhus o Puphamanojiod."
  26,220,"Mata-an naya! A Sukani­yan so Puphakanug, a Mata-o."
  26,221,"Ba Ko rukano Phanothola, so tao a puthupadan o manga Shai­ tan?"
  26,222,"Puthupad ko oman bo­ khag, a baradosa,"
  26,223,"A tatandangan niran sa Pamamakinugan (so manga Shai­tan), na so kadakulan kiran na man­ ga bokhag."
  26,224,"Na so manga Pababayok,­ na Phagonotan siran o Miyangada­ dadag:"
  26,225,"Bangka da mailai a Mata-an! A siran na puphuromparompak sir­an ko oman i labowai?"
  26,226,"Go Mata-an a siran na gi-i ran Tharo-on so di ran Punggolao­ la-an,-"
  26,227,"Tabiya-on so Miyamara­ tiyaya, go Pinggalubuk iran so man­ga pipiya, go Tiyaduman niran so Allah sa madakul, go siyabut iran a ginawa iran ko oriyan o kiyasalim­boti kiran; na katokawan ndun o siran a manga salimbot o antona-a darpa a khandodan i khandodan niran!"